<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<title>Log in</title>
	<%-   include('.././partials/HeadTags')   %>
</head>
<body>
<!-- <%- include('.././partials/koreanHeaderElement') %> -->
<div class="">

	<div class='forms-logo'></div>

	<div class="login local-card shadow">
		<h1 class='title local-mb-8'>로그인</h1>
		<!-- <div class='local-alert danger'>Email already exists!!!</div> -->
		<form action="/auth/login" method="POST">
			<input type="email" name="email" class="form-control local-mt-2" placeholder="이메일을 입력하십시오">
			<input type="password" name="password" class="form-control local-mt-2" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하십시오">
			<button class="local-btn login-btn local-mt-2 local-btn-primary">로그인</button>
		</form>
		<a href='/resetPassword?lang=kr' class="mt-2 links">비밀번호를 잊어 버렸습니까?</a>
		<a href='/register?lang=kr' class="mt-2 links float-right">계정이 없습니까?</a>
		<p class="text-center">또는:</p>
		<a href='/auth/google'>
			<button class="local-btn local-mt-2 google-btn"><i class="fab fa-google mr-2 text-white"></i>Google로 로그인</button>
		</a>
		<a href="/auth/github">
			<button class="local-btn local-mt-2 github-btn"><i class="fab fa-github mr-2 text-white"></i>Github로 로그인</button>
		</a>
		<a href='/auth/linkedin'>
			<button class="local-btn local-mt-2 linkedin-btn"><i class="fab fa-linkedin mr-2 text-white"></i>링크드 인으로 로그인</button>
		</a>
	</div>
	<center>
		<ul class="footer-list local-mt-4">
			<li class='footer-list-item'>서비스 약관</li>
			<li class='footer-list-item'>개인 정보 정책</li>
			<li class='footer-list-item'>어떻게 작동합?</li>
		</ul>
	</center>
	<div class="svgs">
		<div class="svg svg-one"></div>
		<div class="svg svg-second"></div>
	</div>
</div>
</body>
<%-   include('.././partials/ScriptTags')   %>
</html>